      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu pa-augſtini winna\nPrettineeku labbo Rohku/ tu ee-\npreeze wiſſus winna Eenaidnee-\nkus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu effiarri winna Soh-\nbina Afuini atxehtmis/ un ne\nleez winnu Karrā pastahweht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu leeź winna Glihtu-\nnu mittetees/ un nogahs winna\nGohda-Krebslu pee Semines.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu pa-ihſini winna Jan-\nnibas Deenas/ tu apfeds winnu\nar Kannu/Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zik ilgt ak KUNGS!\ngribbees tu muhscham apſlehyp-\ntees? woj tad tawa Bahrsiba ta\nta ugguns degs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Beeminni/ tahds mans\nMuhsch irr/ kapehz buhzi tu wiſ-\nfns Zilweka Behrnus welti rad-\ndijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kursch Zilweks dsihwo/\nkas to Nahivi ne redsehs? kas\ntawu Dwehteli isglahbj no ta\nKappa Warras/Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 50,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS/ kur irr tawas\npreekſchajas Schehlastibas/ ko\ntu Dahwidain eſt pee tawas\nPeetizzibas fwelrejs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Beeminni/ ak KUNGS!\ntawu Kalpu Rauna/ ko es fawā\nAsoti nefu/ no wiſſahm leelahm\nTautahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar ko KUNGS tawi\nEenaidneeki neewa/ ar ko tee ta-\nwa Swaidita Pehdas neewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Glauehrs lat ter tas\nKUNGS muhschigi/ Amen/\nAmen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XC. Dseesma.\nWeena Euhd ſechanas un Mahzičhanas Dseef-\nma Mohsus/ no kurrenes ta Nahwe nah-\nloht: 2/3. Un favehz ta Zilweku Oshwo-\nſchana tik ihſa un behdiga effu: 7/8. Ar\nweenu Luhgſchana/ ka Deews mums to grib-\nbetu likt afs iht/un ar jawu Swehtumu klaht\nstahweht: 12.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eena Luhgſchana Moh-\nsus ta Deewa Wihra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS/ tu effi\nmums par Patwerumnu us Rad-\ndu Raddeim/ pirms tee Kalnt\ntappufchi/ un tu to Semmi un\nto Pasauli bij fataifijs/ effi\ntu muhschigi muhscham tas\nSTIPRAJS DEEWS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas tu tohs Zilwekus par\nPthſchleem darri/ un fakki: At-\ngreeseetees atpakkaz juhs Zilwe-\nën Behrni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tuhkſtoſchi Gaddi irr\ntawa Preekſchā/ itt ka ta Dee-\nna/ kas wakkar pagahjuti/ un ka\nweenas Nakts-Waktis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "* Tu apnemm tohs ta patt\nka Bluhti/ tee irr itt ka Meegs/\ntee irr Agruma ta patt ka Sah-\nle/ kas farwihst.\n* Eebr: Wall: tà : Tu apflazzini tohs irckā\nar stipru Lectu, tee aismeeg, Rihtā irr tee ka\nSahle, kas atspirgstahs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas Rihtā falto/ un tad\natjekt/ un Wakkarā tohp no-\nplanta/ un kalst.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo zaur tawu Duſmibu\nmehs isnihkſtam/ un zaur tawu\nBahrsibu tohpain mehsisbreedeti,\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu leeź muhsus Noseegu-\nmuś\n"
    }
  ],
